{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllBarComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent03BarB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:opacities:effects:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/effects","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/opacities","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/sizes"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/BarComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"BarComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and effects (from "},{"code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeBarComponentTokensProviderC","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}],"symbolKind":"class"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for bar component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomBarComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the bar component tokens you want.","","        override var colorBgOpaque: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.bgTertiary }","","        override var effectBgBlur: EffectSemanticToken { EffectRawTokens.blur320 }","","        override var borderRadiusCurrentIndicatorCustomTop: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusPill }","","        override var sizeWidthCurrentIndicatorCustomBottom: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._650 }","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomBarComponentTokensProvider: BarComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomBBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(bar: CustomBarComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(bar: CustomBarComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBordersSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeEffectSemanticTokensProvider for effects","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider for opacities","    let barComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own providers","    let barComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider(","                    sizes: CustomSizesSemanticTokensProvider(),","                    colors: CustomColorsSemanticTokensProvider(), ...)"]},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.22.0"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/s9EscapableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","title":"Swift.Escapable"}